title: DSC106 Project 2
description: In this project, mouse data is visualized in both accurate and deceptive ways to observe the impacts of certain deception techniques.

title: DSC106 Project 1
description: In this project, a visualization is constructed on climate data to observe the impacts of descriptive techniques.

title: DSC80 Final Project
description: A competitive League of Legends dataset is examined on the impact of creep score/minute for winning games, and then a model is created to predict this metric based on other variables.

title: Optimal Fantasy Drafter
description: This project compared the best possible fantasy draft team with a user's personal draft team, calculating the pick accuracy.

title: Stat Screwed
description: This project calculates how lucky a player got with leveling their characters' random stats in the Fire Emblem game series.
